Start the application in Android Studio.

To add a new item in the inventory, click on the "Add" button.
In the form, enter the GTIN, the name (optional) and the expiry date of the item you want to add.

To modify the expiry date of an already existing item, click on the "Add" button.
In the form, enter the GTIN, the name (optional) and the new expiry date.

Click on the "Submit" button to send the form.
Click on the "Cancel" button if you don't want to add anything.

To reset the inventory, click on the "Reset" button.
